element.name: Motorway Mayhem M1 J5 (Irelands First) by Windsockers, Traditional Cache (1.5/1.5)

long-description.p:
A quick cache and dash at Ireland's first motorway service station which opened this week.
Motorway Mayhem caches are designed to provide fairly easy drive-by caches for travellers who are in need of a break.
You can access this cache from Junction 5 at both the North and South bound exits.
The cache is a magnetic micro container please rehide it with care to prevent muggles from discovering its location
